<div class="min-h-screen bg-white">
  <div class="relative isolate px-6 pt-14 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl py-32">
      <div data-landing-target="fadeIn">
        <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight text-black mb-8">
          BETTER DECISIONS, BETTER RESULTS
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl leading-8 text-gray-800">
          Tech companies struggle with tough choices: fix bugs or build features? Invest in innovation or improve existing tools? Voqua helps engineering and product teams make smarter decisions about where to focus their limited time and resources.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <a href="/users/sign_up" class="px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white bg-black hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all duration-300 rounded-none">
            START FREE NOW
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:hello@voqua.io" class="px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-black border-2 border-black hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 rounded-none">
            ENTERPRISE SUPPORT
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-24 bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black" data-transition-enter="transition ease-out duration-500" data-transition-enter-start="opacity-0 translate-y-4" data-transition-enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-black mb-8">HOW VOQUA WORKS</h2>

          <div class="mb-8">
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
              <%= image_tag "demo.png", class: "border-2 border-black max-w-full h-auto", alt: "Quadratic Voting Demo" %>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-800 text-center font-bold">Real example: A product team deciding what to build next in just one day</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
              <div class="h-12 w-12 flex-none bg-black text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black">LIST YOUR OPTIONS</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-800">Add what your team needs to decide on - bug fixes, new features, tech improvements, or innovation projects.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
              <div class="h-12 w-12 flex-none bg-black text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black">VOTE WITH POINTS</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-800">Team members spend points on what matters most to them. The more points they spend on one option, the more it costs - showing how strongly they really feel.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
              <div class="h-12 w-12 flex-none bg-black text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black">GET CLEAR RESULTS</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-800">See exactly what your team values most. End debates with data that shows where to focus your resources for the biggest impact.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 bg-black text-white p-8" data-transition-enter="transition ease-out duration-500" data-transition-enter-start="opacity-0 translate-y-4" data-transition-enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4">BUILT FOR TECH LEADERS</h2>
          <p class="text-lg">
            Our platform helps engineering managers, product managers, and team leads make better decisions about where to invest their team's time and energy.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mr-3 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
              <p class="text-lg">Cut through bottlenecks and get projects moving</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mr-3 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
              <p class="text-lg">Find the right balance between fixing old code and building new features</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mr-3 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
              <p class="text-lg">Stop overloading your teams and distribute work more effectively</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="mailto:hello@voqua.io" class="px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-black bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all duration-300 rounded-none inline-block">
              TALK TO OUR TEAM
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16" data-transition-enter="transition ease-out duration-500 delay-[300ms]" data-transition-enter-start="opacity-0" data-transition-enter-end="opacity-100">
          <p class="text-base text-gray-800 font-bold">
            Questions about Voqua? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@voqua.io" class="text-black hover:underline">hello@voqua.io</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
